SQL_STMT_U.val: Select Top 1 LineNum From ACQ1 Where DocEntry = :1 Order By LineNum DESC
Select DocEntry From OACQ Where DocEntry in (:1)
Select DocEntry, PostDate,Comments,DocStatus,PIndicator,DocTotal,AssetDate,DataSource From OACQ Where DataSource = 'M' and bplid=:1
Select count(0) jml,sum(DocTotal) total From OACQ Where DataSource = 'M' and bplid=:1
Select count(0) jml,sum(APC) total From ACQ1 Where DocEntry = :1

select ROW_NUMBER() over (order by Itemcode) as 'No', ItemCode,ItemName,CASE WHEN T0.ItemType = 'F' THEN 'Fixed Assets' WHEN T0.ItemType = 'I' THEN 'Items' WHEN T0.ItemType = 'L' THEN 'Labor' WHEN T0.ItemType = 'T' THEN 'Travel' END as 'Item Type', T1.ItmsGrpNam as 'Item Group', CASE WHEN GLMethod = 'L' THEN 'Item' WHEN GLMethod = 'W' THEN 'Warehouse' WHEN GLMethod = 'C' THEN 'Group' END AS 'GLMethod' from OITM (nolock) T0 left join OITB (nolock) T1 on T0.ItmsGrpCod=T1.ItmsGrpCod Where T0.DataSource='M'

select CardCode as 'BP Number', CardName as 'BP Name', CardType as 'BP Type', T1.GroupName as 'BP Group', CASE WHEN Currency = '##' Then 'All Currency' Else Currency END AS 'Currency', Cellular as 'Mobile Phone', DocEntry as 'Doc Entry', Address from OCRD T0 WITH (NOLOCK) LEFT JOIN OCRG T1 (NOLOCK) on T0.GroupCode=T1.GroupCode where T0.DataSource = 'M'
